Crítica de #UntitledGooseGame
Por #MãeSerpente

Sem inimigos, mortes ou possibilidade de derrota, Untitled Goose Game oferece ainda assim um jogo caótico em que o principal objetivo é perturbar todas as pessoas em seu caminho. O protagonista — um ganso — deve roubar itens e atrapalhar os humanos em suas tarefas diárias, de modo a atravessar a cidade rumo a seu misterioso destino final. Dotado apenas das habilidades básicas de um ganso — correr, grasnar, agarrar objetos com o bico — o jogador deve encontrar soluções criativas para uma lista de missões. A arte gráfica e edição de sons inspiradas em desenhos animados ajuda a ressaltar a comédia das situações, ao mesmo tempo em que a ausência de interrupções ajuda a criar a imersão necessária para que Untitled Goose Game se torne um jogo extremamente divertido, em que é possível explorar diferentes maneiras de ser o ganso mais travesso e incômodo do mundo. Muito mais do que uma boa piada, esse é um jogo que demonstra como é possível fazer com que todos os elementos de uma obra ressoem uns com os outros, além de indicar que muito ainda pode ser feito em relação a videogames, de um jeito único e inesperado.

title: Dragon Ball FighterZ DLC - Gogeta

caption.text:
The new Gogeta DLC dropped on Thursday, September 26 and is now playable.

Gogeta is the fusion of Vegeta and Goku after using the Fusion Dance, who was first introduced in 1995’s Dragon Ball Z: Fusion Reborn but not made canon until the 2018 Dragon Ball Super: Broly film.

caption.text:
The temptation won over me and here it is! Nintendo Switch Lite! And because I really love Pompompurin I decided to take the Yellow, hehe! 💛

The first game I will indulge is Nightshade! One of the reasons why I decided to buy a Switch Lite is because of the otome games! And of course the continuation of the Pokemon game franchise after the 3DS line hehe! 💛

Why I decided to buy the Switch Lite instead of the Original Switch v2: There is only one reason, portability. I'm always on the go and I barely even play console games at home, mainly because I always arrive home so late (commonly 10pm). Switch Lite is more portable for me because of its size and lightweight, I can easily bring it out when I'm inside the train. And because I always used a lady's bag at work, its size will not be a problem when I put it inside! Hehe! 💛

Finally on that HORI hype. Yeah, it's good.

So I beat the new Gunvolt.. I’ve never been a fan of this series but it’s the closest thing I get to MegaMan Zero / MegaMan ZX these days. Alas I give it a 4 out of 10 game play is EXTREMELY EASY the mechanics 100% abusable and you basically are INVINCIBLE most of the play through.. no literally invincible as long as Coppen has a Bullet left it will absorb the attack leaving no damage... you double tap *Down* twice and you regenerate ALL BULLETS in less than 2 seconds so let’s say a BOSS *dashes* through you... you take no damage cause you have bullets.. before the BOSS charges again you double tap *Down*.. no damage rinse repeat till last boss... not a very good design if anything another failure by Keji inafune *disrespect intended*... also what is Keji and his teams problem? There’s like... several NAKED under aged girls... sick bastards.😑 / the biggest problem I have with this game is it teaches you to abuse the BULLET system or encourages it however you want to put it and all through out the game there’s *Some* attack’s that your bullets can’t block *hardly any though* and when you get use to it the *Final boss* ALL of his attacks go through your bullet system so that mechanic has no place in that fight.. so you basically mastered it for nothing so that the final boss can *Create the ILLUSION* that it’s hard but really it was a GIMP way for the devs to give you a shitty final fight and master that pointless system. I could go into even more detail but I’m sure I’ve upset some man children already. 😂

caption.text:
New take on an old adventure 🏝🐋 I did some really fun shots of this amiibo for @nintendo and here are a couple of them. I hope you enjoy. Happy gaming Hylians. 
I would also like to state that from here on out I’m going to be taking more breaks from here in general. It’s good for me and my mental health. I have other things to focus on. Positive things. Career things. Things that matter in terms of healing and growth. I appreciate your support through my ups and downs. I also wanted to give the biggest thank you for all the kind messages. To be open with you, I almost didn’t make it Saturday. I make mistakes. I say things I don’t mean. I trusted the wrong people. People I considered friends and I have tried to move on from it for a long time. I again, apologize for my past. I wish you a great weekend 🍁 #nintendo #linksawakening #zelda #toyphotography #amiibo #tokyootakumode #nintendoswitch
Links Awakening Limited Edition #nintendoswitch #nintendo #zelda #linksawakening

No dia 25 de setembro houve simplesmente mais de 10 milhões de downloads do jogo apenas na Play Store (loja de apps do Android). Ou seja, se somarmos ainda os usuários do SO iOS, teremos um volume muito maior e isso é incrível!

@peta

#nintendoswitch #pokemon #mariokart #nintendo#thelegendofzelda #breathofthewild #videogame#supermario #starfox #fzero #playstation #xbox#smashbros #pikachu #earthbound #yoshi#ganondorf #zelda #link #donkeykong#yoshisisland #nintendoswitchmini #supernintendo#retro #nintendomeemes

FIFA sempre foi um grande game e nos últimos anos ele dominou o cenário de jogos de esportes nos videogames, porém, já não é de hoje que jogadores vem reclamando das poucas novidades no jogo em seu modo off-line e das práticas abusivas em seu modo online que sempre dividiu opiniões entre os fãs. Com o lançamento do FIFA2020, as opiniões ainda continuam divididas, já que o "Modo Volta" futebol de rua (famoso Fifa Street) não era lá o que os fãs queriam, afinal de contas seu concorrente Pro evolution Soccer vem trazendo muitas novidades em ralação aos anos anteriores, O destaque principal vai para jogabilidade que está cada vez mais real, algo que os fãs de FIFA viram o game  perder com o passar dos anos. Mas a pergunta que não quer calar é: FIFA vai se encontrar e manterá o seu reinado ou Pro Evolution Soccer irá depois de anos voltar a ser o queridinho dos jogadores? Comente 🗨️ E não deixe de seguir a @99fichas para ficar por dentro do mundo dos games 🎮

caption.text:
Who else is eagerly awaiting more news about Beyond Good and Evil 2?? 🙋 Beyond Good and Evil is one of my favourite games of all time and it feels like we've been waiting literally FOREVER for the next one 😭 It's been a long and messy road but I'm still hopeful that the next game will deliver!⁣
⁣
What's a game you've been anticipating for a really heckin long time??

So, I finished this gorgeous remake of Link’s Awakening a couple days ago and just have so many positive things to say about it.  The overworld tilt-shift aesthetic is easily one of my favorite things about it.  Link’s Awakening DX was the first Zelda game I ever beat so this title does hold a special place to my heart.  It’s a near perfect remake that is so easy to recommend anyone to pick up and play; you won’t regret it.  But for all of its beauty and stylistic direction, it’s not without its faults.  Really just one though; it definitely suffers from some frame rate drop when cutting grass too quickly (especially when just transitioning a screen) and in the graveyard area with the crows.  Not every time either, just every once in a while (in my experience at least.  Keep in mind, I played it strictly handheld and perhaps that played a part in it.  Regardless, it’s such a stunning and enjoyable game!  Whether this is your first trip to Koholint Island or your umpteenth visit, this is certainly a title worth picking up for anyone!  Just cut the owl a break, he’s just trying to help 😅.

Okay, here's the question, digital or physical?  Do you still buy cartridges for your games?  OR do you buy download codes?  If I buy the cartridge, I can share it, or resell it on eBay, but I have to got to the store or wait a day for it to arrive, and I can forget it while traveling.  Buy the download code and I don’t have to go shopping, or wait for Amazon to deliver it, the game is always on my switch, but I can't share it or resell it.  Convenience and instant availability?  Or Flexibility and resale?

caption.text:
The Messenger Exclusive Physical Switch Cartridge by @specialreservegames (Nintendo Switch, 2019)

The Messenger is an action-platform game developed by the independent Quebec-based studio Sabotage Studio and published by Devolver Digital. It was released on Microsoft Windows and Nintendo Switch on August 30, 2018.

The game presents itself as a simple tribute to 8-bit retro action-platformer in which the player controls a Ninja-like warrior sent on an important mission to deliver a magical scroll atop a distant eastern Mountain. During his adventures, the ninja unlocks new abilities such as climbing walls, throwing magical shurikens, gliding and a Rope Dart. The game also uses a mechanic called "Cloudstepping" (gaining additional height from enemies while killing them). During the game, the player unlocks the power to travel into the future, effectively transforming the game into a 16-bit era metroidvania game, where new paths unlock through the finding of secret passages and artifacts.

The Messenger had me hooked from the first moment. It is in my opinion one of the best indie games available on the Switch. It's entertaining, refreshing and very challenging. The story is well written with plot twists throughout the game. The visuals are gorgeous and the transitions from 8bit to 16bit are smooth and a pleasure to watch. The soundtrack is fantastic. The characters are well designed and the dialogue is smart and sprinkled with a lot of humour and references to retro games of the 8bit era. From side-scroller to metroidvania, the game is unique and has it's own identity standing out from the crowd. This game is a must-have for every retro games lover

caption.text:
Nintendo в своём репертуаре🤦‍♂️! На днях вышло переиздание первой части Ni no Kuni - хорошая анимированная сказка от LEVEL5, создавших серию квестов Professor Layton для портативок DS и 3DS, а также потрясающий «аналог» покемонов под названием Yo-kay Watch😍 для 3DS и Switch.
В общем, игра отличная👏, но сейчас не об этом…
Меня смущает разница в цене между версиями для PS4 и Switch😏.
Почему на консоли от Нинтендо опять дороже?

Скорее всего фанаты сыча приведут стандартные доводы:
1) «Зато портатив»
А если я хочу чисто дома играть, то мне скинут цену до уровня плойки? Не думаю, с каждого снимут штаны в равной мере😔;
2) «Сложнее архитектура и мощности меньше, поэтому надо дольше работать над версией сыча».
А мои ли это проблемы? Я пользователь и меня это не должно волновать! Нинтендо решили сделать такую архитектуру, вот пускай сами заморачиваются и субсидируют за свой счёт разработку. Я как пользователь вижу только урезанную графику, меньшее количество кадров и ещё должен радуясь сметать всё с прилавков? Хрен они угадали😠!;
3) «Это не Нинтендо цены выставляет, а издатель»
Опять-таки, почему я должен разбираться в таких тонкостях? Я вижу выше ценник и мне пофиг, кто виноват в этом. Нинтендо обладают нужными рычагами давления на издателя и могли легко скорректировать цену, чтобы такие как я «умники» не осуждали их честное имя.
Вывод: им класть на мнение людей и они из раза в раз сами заряжают космические ценники и не имеют ничего против таких же действий от издателей😢. Прямо сейчас покупать игру я бы всё равно не стал, так как ещё не прошёл ремейк Зельды и не начинал Astral Chain (расскажу о них позже😉), а потом посмотрим, если скинут на версию для сыча, то куплю на него, а если нет, то на плойку👌, ибо я не терпила и не собираюсь на автомате наполнять карманы какой-то одной компании из-за фанатичной любви.

Фанаты, помните☝️, что именно вы формируете ценовую политику изначально, а не Нинтендо! Это вы скупаете всё, не обращая внимания на ценник, поэтому большая «N» впаривает ремейк портативной короткой Зельды по цене новой игры, завышает ценник на аналогичные версии игр в сравнении с конкурентами и не снижает цены на старые игры годами… ГОДАМИ, Карл😳

preview_comments.text: @moonkana_ La tentation était trop forte pour moi ! Déjà DQ XI est excellent mais les ajouts sont vraiment pas anecdotiques ! Les voix japs, la musique de DQ VII, le mode 2D, les nouvelles missions qui se concentre sur les membres du groupe, et le tout en portable pour des centaines et des centaines d'heures...bah c'est (re)passage en caisse ! ❤️

@joo_hwann Je savais que tu le reprendrait aussi 👌🏻 La proposition est trop alléchante pour les fans de la série (et ceux qui vont inévitablement le devenir pour le coup !), ça fait tellement plaisir de sortir la portable dans le lit 😎

caption.text:
Hace un par de días terminé la secuela de SteamWorld Dig, un juego de robots mineros, con una estética 2D muy bonita.

Título: SteamWorld Dig 2
Plataforma: Xbox One
Fecha: 25 de septiembre de 2019
Horas: 9
Logros: 560G

He de decir que el primer juego me gustó mucho, y que este, aún manteniendo la esencia del anterior, lo mejora.

En esta ocasión, encarnamos a la hermana del anterior protagonista, quien emprende una larga y profunda (por lo mucho que tiene que cavar 😂) búsqueda de su hermano, para lo que contará con un interesante arsenal de dispositivos que le facilitarán mucho las cosas.

Si os gustan los juegos de plataformas, que no buscan rizar el rizo, os recomiendo este juego.

caption.text:
娘の誕生日は10月末。
一年以上前から、「Switchがほしい！」と言い出した娘。
「来年に新しいバージョンが出るらしいから、それまで待って！」と、我慢させることはや一年。
本日、誕生日プレゼントがやってきた〜🎁
大人の事情により、一ヶ月早く、
大人の事情により、パパママ好みの仕様だけど✨
・
旦那がやり始めたのを横で見ていて、
声があるのがとても新鮮！
オープニングのムービーで、テオが流れてきた赤子を抱き上げる時の緒方賢一さんの声が予想通りピッタリすぎて素敵すぎて、それだけで涙腺刺激される。
オケの音楽がカッコいい！
・
娘がやりたいソフトは明後日に購入予定。
・
私はドラクエウォークで歩かねばならないし、
DSのドラクエ7は途中で放置したままだし、
映画観てまたやり始めたスマホ版5も中途半端だし、
懐かしい、ゼルダの「夢をみる島」は絶対やりたいし、
11はさすがにまだ覚えてるし、
11sはしばらくできないなぁ。
圧倒的に時間が足りなさすぎる…。
・
私がドラクエを初めて1人でプレイしたのは、
小3か4くらいでドラクエ2を。
娘は現在小3なので、この11sでドラクエプレイデビューにちょうどいいかも。
難しいかな？
#nintendoswitch 
#ニンテンドースイッチ
#ロトエディション 
#ドラゴンクエスト
#ドラゴンクエスト11s
#娘の誕生日プレゼント
#なはず

CONDIVIDI NELLE STORIE ⬇️ Sebbene i dialoghi di Skyrim non godano di spiccata qualità letteraria, ci sono dei passaggi suggestivi persino estrapolati dal contesto di gioco. Una delle grandi sfide per The Elder Scrolls VI, sarà quella di riportare nella formula la profondità di linguaggio e di contenuto, ovvero il cuore del Fantasy Epico. Non solo ci auguriamo che Bethesda si riveli in grado di assimilare i paradigmi delle esperienze a mondo aperto di recente ideazione, ma anche che riesca a integrare i passaggi parlati nella continuità del percorso ludico. Anziché riservare istanze separate allo scambio di battute, oppure relegare il giocatore al ruolo di spettatore davanti a scene dalla impacciata teatralità, TES VI dovrebbe proporre un equilibrio tra linearità narrativa ed esperienza personale similare a quello di Red Dead Redemption 2. 
Tanto si può riflettere, tanto si può dire, ma Instagram non è la sede giusta. Troveremo il modo di discuterne insieme. 
Commenta con la tua opinione, tagga un amico e condividi. Inoltre, unisciti al gruppo Telegram di Gamerversum. Xbox Games With Gold: Confira os games grátis do mês de outubro

Ainda é possível resgatar alguns títulos do mês de setembro

A Microsoft revelou os games gratuitos do mês de Outubro de 2019 para os assinantes do serviço Xbox Live Gold. Entre os destaques estão Friday the 13th e Tembo the Badass Elephant.

Confira todos os games a seguir: * Tembo the Badass Elephant: Disponível entre 1 e 31 de outubro no Xbox * OneFriday the 13th: The Game: Disponível entre 16 de outubro e 15 de novembro no Xbox * OneDisney Bolt: Disponível entre os dias 1 e 15 de outubro para Xbox One e Xbox 360 * Ninja Gaiden 3: Razor’s Edge: Disponível entre 16 e 31 de outubro para Xbox One e Xbox 360.

Ainda é possível baixar Hitman, We Were Here e Tekken Tag Tournament 2 gratuitamente por meio dos Games with Gold de setembro.

Siga-nos pelas redes sociais: Instagram, Facebook e Twitter. Cometem e compartilhem com seus amigos.
